data.text: @Coachterreault @WPTV @weatherchannel Thanks again.  You are awesome.   What’s up w Ericka Jane?  She’s off the show?  I’m missing everything w this storm

I was working the other day in an amazing condo building in Boca. The engineer said he'd be riding the storm out onsite. They have generators that will run the entire building at 100%, with everyone in residence (only about 10% are in residence this time of year) for two weeks.

So I'm in the orange, tropical storm warning (if you look closely at the West Palm Beach you see a little bump on the edge of Florida, that's basically me). The island and offshore are looking at hurricane winds.  When we say "the island" we're talking about the barrier island https://t.co/1bsgA64wXv

@GulfStreamViews Wow! Katrina survivor, huh. This cat 5 is being compared to Andrew. We'll see. It's already starting to fall apart. The Haitians here have no concept of 'emergency vehicles' only on the road 'til  after the storm. Sad but true.
This storm is at a stand still due to the air currents from the north & south
This storm got stronger & hasn’t moved for 3 hours. Repaired the second eye
